# December 8, 2023 - Notes

## Gameplan

### 1. Use the Purple **Get Sensors Data** API call to get a list of sensors which fall into geographic bounds of Denver.

[API Reference](https://api.purpleair.com/#api-sensors-get-sensors-data)

Fields To Include

`name,model,hardware,latitude,longitude,altitude,position_rating,led_brightness,firmware_version,uptime,pa_latency,memory,last_seen,last_modified,date_created,channel_state,channel_flags,channel_flags_manual,channel_flags_auto, confidence,confidence_manual,confidence_auto,temperature,humidity,pressure,voc`

Location Type: `location_type=0`

Corners:

* Northwest:  39.930106째N 105.276691째W
* Southest:   39.547914째N 104.650771째W

```
GET https://api.purpleair.com/v1/sensors?fields=name%2Cmodel%2Chardware%2Clatitude%2Clongitude%2Caltitude%2Cposition_rating%2Cled_brightness%2Cfirmware_version%2Cuptime%2Cpa_latency%2Cmemory%2Clast_seen%2Clast_modified%2Cdate_created%2Cchannel_state%2Cchannel_flags%2Cchannel_flags_manual%2Cchannel_flags_auto%2C%20confidence%2Cconfidence_manual%2Cconfidence_auto%2Ctemperature%2Chumidity%2Cpressure%2Cvoc&location_type=0&nwlng=-105.276691&nwlat=39.930106&selng=-104.650771&selat=39.547914 HTTP/1.1
X-API-Key: D1011E96-959D-11EE-8616-42010A80000B
```
